    <dashboard _.fcp.AccessibleZoneTabOrder.true...enable-sort-zone-taborder='true' name='Insights &amp; Recommendations'>
      <style />
      <size sizing-mode='automatic' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='4' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone forceUpdate='true' h='97856' id='3' type-v2='text' w='99002' x='499' y='1072'>
            <formatted-text>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='2'>Walmart Product Performance Analysis</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='2'>Key Findings</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='2'>1. Customer Satisfaction is Strong</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='2'>Most products have ratings between 4.0 and 5.0. </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='2'>Customer sentiment toward Walmart products is generally positive. </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='2'>2. Customer Engagement is Uneven</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='2'>A small number of products receive the majority of reviews. </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='2'>Many highly rated products receive relatively little customer attention. </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='2'>3. Ratings Do Not Strongly Drive Engagement</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='2'>Products with high ratings do not always have high review volumes. </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='2'>Customer engagement appears to be influenced by additional factors such as visibility, promotions, and brand recognition. </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='2'>4. Price Has Limited Impact on Ratings</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='2'>Higher-priced products do not consistently achieve better ratings. </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='2'>Product value and customer experience appear more important than price alone. </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='2'>5. Category Performance Varies</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='2'>Beauty and Personal Care categories generate the highest engagement. </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='2'>Some categories achieve strong ratings despite lower review volumes. </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='2'>6. Top Brands Identified Using Weighted Performance Metrics</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='2'>Affresh </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='2'>Native </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='2'>Glad </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='2'>These brands consistently perform well when both customer satisfaction and engagement are considered.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='2'>Recommendations</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='2'>Recommendation 1</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='2'>Promote highly rated products with low engagement through better visibility and targeted marketing.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='2'>Recommendation 2</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='2'>Use weighted performance metrics instead of ratings alone when evaluating product and brand performance.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='2'>Recommendation 3</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='2'>Analyze top-performing brands and replicate successful strategies across lower-performing products.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='2'>Recommendation 4</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='2'>Focus on customer value, quality, and experience rather than relying solely on pricing strategies. </run>
            </formatted-text>
            <zone-style>
              <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
              <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
              <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
              <format attr='margin' value='4' />
            </zone-style>
          </zone>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <format attr='margin' value='8' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
      </zones>
