                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontsize='11'>• High ratings do not always generate high engagement.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontsize='11'>• Some highly rated products receive very few reviews.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontsize='11'>• Product price shows weak correlation with customer satisfaction.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontsize='11'>• Customers appear to value product quality more than price.</run>
